<Pair><Serial>1</Serial><Id>1093266792948</Id><Source>Xuan Zang, Possibly China's Greatest Translator</Source><Target>Xuan Zang, probabilmente il più grande traduttore cinese</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020919T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266792948</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>2</Serial><Id>1093266793131</Id><Source>His 10-stage quality control process initiated more than 1300 years ago is far more thorough and exacting than any existing today.</Source><Target>Il suo metodo di controllo di qualità in 10 fasi risale a più di 1300 anni fa ed è molto più accurato e preciso di qualsiasi metodo attuale.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793131</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>3</Serial><Id>1093266793344</Id><Source>Introduction</Source><Target>Introduzione</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793344</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>4</Serial><Id>1093266793385</Id><Source>Every Chinese, young and old, within and outside China, knows the classical language rendering of the exploits of Xuan Zang, the pious Tang dynasty monk and his three storybook disciples, the indestructible Monkey King, the Great Sage; Brother Pig, the Eight Denials (of Buddhism) and Sand Monk, the third disciple. </Source><Target>I Cinesi d'ogni età, in Cina e fuori di essa, conoscono la versione in cinese classico delle avventure di Xuan Zang, il pio monaco buddista della dinastia Tang e dei suoi tre leggendari discepoli, l'indistruttibile Re Scimmia, il Grande Saggio; il Porcello delle Otto Astinenze (del Buddismo) e Sabbioso, il terzo discepolo. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793385</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>5</Serial><Id>1093266793776</Id><Source>In real life, Xuan Zang was a truly remarkable Buddhist monk. </Source><Target>Nella vita reale, Xuan Zang fu un monaco veramente eccezionale. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793776</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>6</Serial><Id>1093266793860</Id><Source>He traveled on land on the way through hostile and uncharted territory to the birthplace of Buddha in the Indian sub-continent and returned to Chang'an (modern day Xi'an) with a set of Buddhist sutras. </Source><Target>Egli attraversò zone ostili e inesplorate fino a raggiungere il luogo di nascita di Budda, nel subcontinente indiano. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793860</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>7</Serial><Id>1093266794053</Id><Source>The voluminous set of sutras was written in the extremely difficult Sanskrit language. </Source><Target>Fece ritorno a Chang'an (l'attuale Xi'an) con una voluminosa edizione completa di sutra buddisti, scritti nel difficilissimo Sanscrito. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794053</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>8</Serial><Id>1093266794192</Id><Source>Together with his doyens of pupils, he completed the translation of some 75 volumes of the sutras into the equally difficult Chinese languages</Source><Target>In collaborazione con i suoi allievi più esperti, egli tradusse qualcosa come 75 volumi di sutra nelle altrettanto ostiche lingue cinesi. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794192</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>9</Serial><Id>1093266794333</Id><Source>The 10 Stages</Source><Target>Le 10 fasi</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794333</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>10</Serial><Id>1093266794352</Id><Source>Buddhist sutras translated into Chinese prior the Tang dynasty were difficult to comprehend because the first translators were Buddhist monks of non-Han Chinese origin. </Source><Target>Le traduzioni di sutra buddisti anteriori alla dinastia Tang erano di difficile comprensione, giacché i monaci che le avevano tradotte non erano di origine Han.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794352</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>11</Serial><Id>1093266794516</Id><Source>It took China several hundred years to bring forth a selection of Buddhist monks who could master both the Sanskrit language as well as the complex Buddhism doctrines, which were written in Sanskrit. </Source><Target>Ci vollero alcuni secoli prima che in Cina si formasse un gruppo di monaci buddisti in grado di dominare sia le complesse dottrine buddiste sia il sanscrito, lingua in cui queste furono scritte. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794516</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>12</Serial><Id>1093266794692</Id><Source>And Xuan Zang was recognized as foremost among them. </Source><Target>Xuan Zang, considerato il massimo rappresentante di questo gruppo, </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794692</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>13</Serial><Id>1093266794763</Id><Source>He was appointed chief of the Tang dynasty imperial translation center. </Source><Target>fu nominato direttore del centro di traduzione della dinastia imperiale Tang.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794763</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>14</Serial><Id>1093266794853</Id><Source>It was he who designed and implemented a translation workflow that would guarantee the quality of the final product. </Source><Target>Fu lui a creare e a mettere a punto un sistema di lavoro per garantire la qualità del prodotto finale.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794853</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>15</Serial><Id>1093266794974</Id><Source>The process detailed below is well worth adopting by any modern day translation team.</Source><Target>Anche ai giorni nostri, il metodo descritto qui sotto può benissimo essere adottato da qualsiasi equipe di traduttori.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794974</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>16</Serial><Id>1093266795125</Id><Source>Stage 1</Source><Target>Fase 1</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795125</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>17</Serial><Id>1093266795138</Id><Source>Master translator and Buddhism expert to jointly study and interpret the original text written in Sanskrit. </Source><Target>Il maestro traduttore e l'esperto di buddismo studiano e interpretano insieme il testo originale sanscrito. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795138</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>18</Serial><Id>1093266795269</Id><Source>It could involve one or more persons.</Source><Target>A questa fase possono partecipare una o più persone.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795269</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>19</Serial><Id>1093266795322</Id><Source>Stage 2</Source><Target>Fase 2</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795322</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>20</Serial><Id>1093266795337</Id><Source>All members of the translation team to attend a recital of the text in question by the Master translator. </Source><Target>Tutti i membri del gruppo di traduzione assistono alla lettura del testo in questione da parte del maestro traduttore, </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795337</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>21</Serial><Id>1093266795525</Id><Source>The purpose is to verify the accuracy of the interpretation undertaken in Stage 1. </Source><Target>allo scopo di verificare l'esattezza di quanto interpretato nella fase 1.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795525</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>22</Serial><Id>1093266795617</Id><Source>A recital is necessary because the scriptures were originally written for recitation.</Source><Target>La lettura è necessaria perché originariamente il testo fu concepito per la recitazione.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795617</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>23</Serial><Id>1093266795725</Id><Source>Stage 3</Source><Target>Fase 3</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795725</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>24</Serial><Id>1093266795739</Id><Source>A team of junior translators produces the first Chinese draft of the Sanskrit text. </Source><Target>Un gruppo di allievi traduttori redige una prima bozza in cinese del testo sanscrito. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795739</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>25</Serial><Id>1093266795838</Id><Source>The draft is a combination of transliteration of Sanskrit terms and standard Chinese.</Source><Target>La bozza è una combinazione di traslitterazione di termini sanscriti e di termini in cinese standard.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795838</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>26</Serial><Id>1093266795952</Id><Source>Stage 4</Source><Target>Fase 4</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795952</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>27</Serial><Id>1093266796006</Id><Source>Production of a complete Chinese version by a senior native Chinese Buddhist monk trained to undertake scripture translation. </Source><Target>Elaborazione di una versione cinese completa a cura un monaco buddista di madrelingua cinese, esperto e specializzato nella traduzione di testi sacri. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796006</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>28</Serial><Id>1093266796174</Id><Source>This is the most important stage in the entire process and it must be undertaken by a monk with an in-depth knowledge of Chinese culture and language.</Source><Target>Questa è la fase più importante dell'intero processo e deve essere affidata a un monaco con una perfetta padronanza della cultura e della lingua cinese.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796174</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>29</Serial><Id>1093266796351</Id><Source>Stage 5</Source><Target>Fase 5</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796351</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>30</Serial><Id>1093266796367</Id><Source>Refinement of sentence structure of the complete Chinese version. </Source><Target>Perfezionamento della struttura delle frasi dell'intera versione cinese. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796367</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>31</Serial><Id>1093266796460</Id><Source>This is a necessary stage because of the vast linguistic differences between the source and target language.</Source><Target>È una fase necessaria, viste le grandi differenze linguistiche tra la lingua di partenza e quella d'arrivo.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796460</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>32</Serial><Id>1093266796587</Id><Source>Stage 6</Source><Target>Fase 6</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796587</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>33</Serial><Id>1093266796604</Id><Source>Reverse translation of the Chinese version into Sanskrit in order to verify the accuracy of the interpretation of the original text. </Source><Target>Traduzione inversa della versione cinese al sanscrito, al fine di verificare l'esattezza dell'interpretazione del testo originale. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796604</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>34</Serial><Id>1093266796755</Id><Source>Mistakes in interpretation are to be promptly rectified in the Chinese version.</Source><Target>Errori d'interpretazione sono immediatamente rettificati nella versione cinese.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796755</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>35</Serial><Id>1093266796864</Id><Source>Stage 7</Source><Target>Fase 7</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796864</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>36</Serial><Id>1093266796880</Id><Source>Review of the verified Chinese version to identify errors in character usage, and refinement of linguistic expressions to improve readability.</Source><Target>Revisione della versione cinese precedentemente controllata, al fine di individuare errori nell'uso di caratteri. Perfezionamento delle espressioni idiomatiche per una migliore leggibilità.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796880</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>37</Serial><Id>1093266797078</Id><Source>Stage 8</Source><Target>Fase 8</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797078</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>38</Serial><Id>1093266797098</Id><Source>Further polishing to improve the literary beauty of the language and adding colors to the otherwise monotonous writings.</Source><Target>Ulteriore revisione per migliorare la qualità letteraria della lingua e per aggiungere coloritura ai testi, che altrimenti potrebbero risultare monotoni. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797098</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>39</Serial><Id>1093266797242</Id><Source>Stage 9</Source><Target>Fase 9</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797242</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>40</Serial><Id>1093266797261</Id><Source>Verification of the audio quality by reciting the translation aloud. </Source><Target>Lettura ad alta voce della traduzione per verificarne la qualità acustica; </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797261</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>41</Serial><Id>1093266797353</Id><Source>The audio effect is important because scriptures are meant for preaching to an audience.</Source><Target>di grande importanza, considerato che le scritture furono concepite per essere recitate in pubblico.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797353</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>42</Serial><Id>1093266797464</Id><Source>Stage 10</Source><Target>Fase 10</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797464</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>43</Serial><Id>1093266797482</Id><Source>Final check by the Master Translator.</Source><Target>Verifica finale da parte del maestro traduttore.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797482</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>44</Serial><Id>1093266797537</Id><Source>Conclusion</Source><Target>Conclusione</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040705T121341Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797537</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>45</Serial><Id>1093266797565</Id><Source>Xuan Zang did a great job in the translation of the Buddhist sutras. </Source><Target>Xuan Zang fece un'eccezionale traduzione dei sutra buddisti. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797565</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>46</Serial><Id>1093266797652</Id><Source>He was able to excel not only was he an outstanding linguist but also he was wholeheartedly committed to the task as a devoted Buddhist with an extraordinary understanding of its contents. </Source><Target>Personaggio fuori del comune, egli non solo fu uno straordinario linguista, ma anche un buddista devoto, che si dedicò con abnegazione a una materia che conosceva a fondo: impegnò, </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101705Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797652</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>47</Serial><Id>1093266797842</Id><Source>Indeed, he dedicated thirteen years of his life to the task. </Source><Target>infatti, ben tredici anni in quest'impresa.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797842</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>48</Serial><Id>1093266797899</Id><Source>And the task was not simply transforming one language into another. </Source><Target>E non si trattava solo di trasformare una lingua in un'altra: per un'efficace divulgazione del Buddismo, </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797899</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>49</Serial><Id>1093266797991</Id><Source>In order to effectively spread Buddhism, the sutras in Chinese would have to be understood by the Chinese devotees. </Source><Target>i sutra in cinese dovevano risultare comprensibili ai fedeli cinesi.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101717Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797991</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>50</Serial><Id>1093266798115</Id><Source>In other words, he had to take into account the marketplace. </Source><Target>In altre parole, bisognava tener conto del mercato. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798115</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>51</Serial><Id>1093266798174</Id><Source>Was it intended for the gentry for whom Buddhism depended for their financial support or was it for the less literate general populace to widen market share or was it for both?</Source><Target>A chi era destinata la traduzione? All'elite dal cui appoggio dipendevano gli interessi del Buddismo, al popolino, allo scopo di incrementare la quota di mercato, oppure ad entrambi?</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>it</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101647Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798174</Prop></Pair>
</Asset>
<Asset package="..\..\Samples\XuanZang.tmx" original="en - ko" source-lang="en" target-lang="ko">
<Pair><Serial>1</Serial><Id>1093266792948</Id><Source>Xuan Zang, Possibly China's Greatest Translator</Source><Target>현장법사(玄奬法師), 중국 최고의 번역가</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020919T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266792948</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>2</Serial><Id>1093266793131</Id><Source>His 10-stage quality control process initiated more than 1300 years ago is far more thorough and exacting than any existing today.</Source><Target>그가 1300여년 전 시작한 10단계 품질 관리 방법은 현존하는 것보다 훨씬 더 철저하고 정확하다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793131</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>3</Serial><Id>1093266793344</Id><Source>Introduction</Source><Target>서론</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793344</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>4</Serial><Id>1093266793385</Id><Source>Every Chinese, young and old, within and outside China, knows the classical language rendering of the exploits of Xuan Zang, the pious Tang dynasty monk and his three storybook disciples, the indestructible Monkey King, the Great Sage; Brother Pig, the Eight Denials (of Buddhism) and Sand Monk, the third disciple. </Source><Target>중국 국내외, 남녀노소를 불문한 모든 중국인들은 당대(唐代, 618-907 AD)의 독실한 승려인 현장법사와 그의 이야기책 속에 나오는 세 명의 제자들, 즉 공(空)을 깨닫는다라는 뜻을 지닌 불멸의 손오공, (불교의) 여덟 가지 계율을 나타내는 저팔계, 세 번째 제자인 사오정이 이루어낸 업적 가운데 고전적인 언어 번역에 대해서 알고 있다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793385</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>5</Serial><Id>1093266793776</Id><Source>In real life, Xuan Zang was a truly remarkable Buddhist monk. </Source><Target>실제로 현장법사는 매우 뛰어난 불교 승려였다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793776</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>6</Serial><Id>1093266793860</Id><Source>He traveled on land on the way through hostile and uncharted territory to the birthplace of Buddha in the Indian sub-continent and returned to Chang'an (modern day Xi'an) with a set of Buddhist sutras. </Source><Target>인도 아대륙(亞大陸)에 있는 부처의 탄생지를 찾기 위해 적대적이고 지도에도 나타나있지 않은 지역들을 거쳐 대륙을 여행했고 일련의 불교 경전을 가지고 장안(현재의 시안(서안, 西安))으로 돌아왔다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793860</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>7</Serial><Id>1093266794053</Id><Source>The voluminous set of sutras was written in the extremely difficult Sanskrit language. </Source><Target>방대한 양의 경전은 극도로 어려운 산스크리트어(범어, 梵語)로 저술되어 있었다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794053</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>8</Serial><Id>1093266794192</Id><Source>Together with his doyens of pupils, he completed the translation of some 75 volumes of the sutras into the equally difficult Chinese languages</Source><Target>그는 오랫동안 수행해온 제자들과 함께 75권이나 되는 경전을 산스크리트어만큼 어려운 중국어로 번역했다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794192</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>9</Serial><Id>1093266794333</Id><Source>The 10 Stages</Source><Target>열 단계</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794333</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>10</Serial><Id>1093266794352</Id><Source>Buddhist sutras translated into Chinese prior the Tang dynasty were difficult to comprehend because the first translators were Buddhist monks of non-Han Chinese origin. </Source><Target>당대 이전에 중국어로 번역된 불교 경전들은 한족(漢族) 출신이 아닌 불교 승려들이 최초로 번역했기 때문에 이해하기 어려웠다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794352</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>11</Serial><Id>1093266794516</Id><Source>It took China several hundred years to bring forth a selection of Buddhist monks who could master both the Sanskrit language as well as the complex Buddhism doctrines, which were written in Sanskrit. </Source><Target>중국은 산스크리트어 뿐만 아니라 산스크리트어로 쓰여진 복잡한 불교의 교리에 정통한 불교 승려들을 배출하는데 수 백년이 걸렸다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794516</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>12</Serial><Id>1093266794692</Id><Source>And Xuan Zang was recognized as foremost among them. </Source><Target>현장법사는 그들 가운데에서도 최고로 인정 받았다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794692</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>13</Serial><Id>1093266794763</Id><Source>He was appointed chief of the Tang dynasty imperial translation center. </Source><Target>그는 당대 황실 번역소(역경원)의 대표자로 임명되었다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794763</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>14</Serial><Id>1093266794853</Id><Source>It was he who designed and implemented a translation workflow that would guarantee the quality of the final product. </Source><Target>최종 완성본의 품질을 보증할 수 있는 번역 작업 과정을 고안해내고 실행한 사람이 바로 그였다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794853</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>15</Serial><Id>1093266794974</Id><Source>The process detailed below is well worth adopting by any modern day translation team.</Source><Target>아래 열거한 과정은 오늘날의 번역 팀도 도입해 볼 만한 가치가 있을 것이다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794974</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>16</Serial><Id>1093266795125</Id><Source>Stage 1</Source><Target>1 단계</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795125</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>17</Serial><Id>1093266795138</Id><Source>Master translator and Buddhism expert to jointly study and interpret the original text written in Sanskrit. </Source><Target>번역 팀장과 불교 전문가가 함께 산스크리트어로 쓰여진 원문을 연구하고 해석한다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795138</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>18</Serial><Id>1093266795269</Id><Source>It could involve one or more persons.</Source><Target>여기에는 한 명 이상의 사람들이 참여할 것이다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795269</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>19</Serial><Id>1093266795322</Id><Source>Stage 2</Source><Target>2 단계</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795322</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>20</Serial><Id>1093266795337</Id><Source>All members of the translation team to attend a recital of the text in question by the Master translator. </Source><Target>번역 팀의 모든 멤버들이 번역 팀장이 문제를 제기한 본문의 낭독에 참여한다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795337</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>21</Serial><Id>1093266795525</Id><Source>The purpose is to verify the accuracy of the interpretation undertaken in Stage 1. </Source><Target>1단계에서 수행한 해석이 정확한지 확인하는 것이 목적이다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795525</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>22</Serial><Id>1093266795617</Id><Source>A recital is necessary because the scriptures were originally written for recitation.</Source><Target>경전들은 원래 낭독하기 위해 쓴 것이기 때문에 낭독이 필수적이다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795617</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>23</Serial><Id>1093266795725</Id><Source>Stage 3</Source><Target>3 단계</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795725</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>24</Serial><Id>1093266795739</Id><Source>A team of junior translators produces the first Chinese draft of the Sanskrit text. </Source><Target>하위 번역팀이 산스크리트어 본문에 대해 중국어 초안을 만든다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795739</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>25</Serial><Id>1093266795838</Id><Source>The draft is a combination of transliteration of Sanskrit terms and standard Chinese.</Source><Target>이 초안에는 산스크리트 용어의 음역(音譯)과 중국 표준어가 결합되어 있다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795838</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>26</Serial><Id>1093266795952</Id><Source>Stage 4</Source><Target>4 단계</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795952</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>27</Serial><Id>1093266796006</Id><Source>Production of a complete Chinese version by a senior native Chinese Buddhist monk trained to undertake scripture translation. </Source><Target>토종 중국인으로 경전 번역에 숙련된 중견 불교 승려에 의한 완전한 중국어판을  작성한다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796006</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>28</Serial><Id>1093266796174</Id><Source>This is the most important stage in the entire process and it must be undertaken by a monk with an in-depth knowledge of Chinese culture and language.</Source><Target>전 과정 중에서 이 단계가 가장 중요하며 중국의 문화와 언어에 대해 심층적인 지식을 가지고 있는 승려가 수행해야만 한다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796174</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>29</Serial><Id>1093266796351</Id><Source>Stage 5</Source><Target>5 단계</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796351</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>30</Serial><Id>1093266796367</Id><Source>Refinement of sentence structure of the complete Chinese version. </Source><Target>완전한 중국어 판의 문장 구조를 다듬는다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796367</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>31</Serial><Id>1093266796460</Id><Source>This is a necessary stage because of the vast linguistic differences between the source and target language.</Source><Target>이 단계는 원문과 목표 언어 사이에 커다란 언어적 차이가 있기 때문에 필수적이다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796460</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>32</Serial><Id>1093266796587</Id><Source>Stage 6</Source><Target>6 단계</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796587</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>33</Serial><Id>1093266796604</Id><Source>Reverse translation of the Chinese version into Sanskrit in order to verify the accuracy of the interpretation of the original text. </Source><Target>원문의 해석이 정확한지 검증하기 위해 중국어 판을 산스크리트어로 거꾸로 번역한다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796604</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>34</Serial><Id>1093266796755</Id><Source>Mistakes in interpretation are to be promptly rectified in the Chinese version.</Source><Target>해석상의 실수를 중국어 판에서 신속하게 수정할 수 있다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796755</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>35</Serial><Id>1093266796864</Id><Source>Stage 7</Source><Target>7 단계</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796864</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>36</Serial><Id>1093266796880</Id><Source>Review of the verified Chinese version to identify errors in character usage, and refinement of linguistic expressions to improve readability.</Source><Target>문자 사용 상의 오류를 찾아내기 위해 검증된 중국어 판을 재검토하고, 보다 읽기 쉽게 하기 위해 언어적 표현을 다듬는다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796880</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>37</Serial><Id>1093266797078</Id><Source>Stage 8</Source><Target>8 단계</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797078</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>38</Serial><Id>1093266797098</Id><Source>Further polishing to improve the literary beauty of the language and adding colors to the otherwise monotonous writings.</Source><Target>언어가 갖는 문학적 아름다움을 높이기 위해 세련되게 다듬기와 단조로운 문장들에 색채를 입힌다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797098</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>39</Serial><Id>1093266797242</Id><Source>Stage 9</Source><Target>9 단계</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797242</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>40</Serial><Id>1093266797261</Id><Source>Verification of the audio quality by reciting the translation aloud. </Source><Target>번역물을 큰소리로 낭독하여 음질을 확인한다. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797261</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>41</Serial><Id>1093266797353</Id><Source>The audio effect is important because scriptures are meant for preaching to an audience.</Source><Target>경전은 청중을 설득하기 위한 것이므로 청각적인 효과가 중요하다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797353</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>42</Serial><Id>1093266797464</Id><Source>Stage 10</Source><Target>10 단계</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797464</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>43</Serial><Id>1093266797482</Id><Source>Final check by the Master Translator.</Source><Target>번역 팀장이 최종 점검한다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797482</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>44</Serial><Id>1093266797537</Id><Source>Conclusion</Source><Target>결론</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040705T121341Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797537</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>45</Serial><Id>1093266797565</Id><Source>Xuan Zang did a great job in the translation of the Buddhist sutras. </Source><Target>현장법사는 불교 경전 번역에서 대단한 위업을 달성했다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797565</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>46</Serial><Id>1093266797652</Id><Source>He was able to excel not only was he an outstanding linguist but also he was wholeheartedly committed to the task as a devoted Buddhist with an extraordinary understanding of its contents. </Source><Target>그는 뛰어난 언어학자였을 뿐만 아니라, 귀의한 불자로서 경전 내용을 정확히 파악하여 전심 전력을 다해 과업을 수행한 뛰어난 사람이었다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101705Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797652</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>47</Serial><Id>1093266797842</Id><Source>Indeed, he dedicated thirteen years of his life to the task. </Source><Target>실제로 그는 이 작업에 13년이라는 세월을 바쳤다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797842</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>48</Serial><Id>1093266797899</Id><Source>And the task was not simply transforming one language into another. </Source><Target>그리고 이 작업은 단순히 하나의 언어를 다른 언어로 바꾸는 것이 아니었다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797899</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>49</Serial><Id>1093266797991</Id><Source>In order to effectively spread Buddhism, the sutras in Chinese would have to be understood by the Chinese devotees. </Source><Target>불교를 효과적으로 전파하기 위해서 중국어 경전을 중국인 신자들이 이해해야만 했다. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101717Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797991</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>50</Serial><Id>1093266798115</Id><Source>In other words, he had to take into account the marketplace. </Source><Target>다시 말해, 그는 속세를 염두에 두어야만 했다. </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798115</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>51</Serial><Id>1093266798174</Id><Source>Was it intended for the gentry for whom Buddhism depended for their financial support or was it for the less literate general populace to widen market share or was it for both?</Source><Target>불교의 재정적인 지원을 맡았던 상류층을 향한 의도였는지, 아니면 불교 전파를 위해 덜 교육 받은 일반 서민들을 향한 의도였는지, 그도 아니면 그 모두를 위한 의도였는지에 대한 의문은 남는다.</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101647Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798174</Prop></Pair>
</Asset>
<Asset package="..\..\Samples\XuanZang.tmx" original="en - zh-cn" source-lang="en" target-lang="zh-cn">
<Pair><Serial>1</Serial><Id>1093266792948</Id><Source>Xuan Zang, Possibly China's Greatest Translator</Source><Target>玄奘，中国最伟大的翻译家</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020919T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266792948</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>2</Serial><Id>1093266793131</Id><Source>His 10-stage quality control process initiated more than 1300 years ago is far more thorough and exacting than any existing today.</Source><Target>1300 多年前，他创立了翻译质量控制的十个步骤，其严谨与精确程度远远超过当今翻译界。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793131</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>3</Serial><Id>1093266793344</Id><Source>Introduction</Source><Target>简介</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793344</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>4</Serial><Id>1093266793385</Id><Source>Every Chinese, young and old, within and outside China, knows the classical language rendering of the exploits of Xuan Zang, the pious Tang dynasty monk and his three storybook disciples, the indestructible Monkey King, the Great Sage; Brother Pig, the Eight Denials (of Buddhism) and Sand Monk, the third disciple. </Source><Target>古今中外，几乎无人不晓唐代高僧玄奘在古代汉语方面所做的贡献，以及他在小说《西游记》中的三位徒弟，大徒弟孙悟空，二徒弟猪八戒和三徒弟沙僧。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793385</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>5</Serial><Id>1093266793776</Id><Source>In real life, Xuan Zang was a truly remarkable Buddhist monk. </Source><Target>在真实生活中，玄奘的确是一个了不起的僧人。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793776</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>6</Serial><Id>1093266793860</Id><Source>He traveled on land on the way through hostile and uncharted territory to the birthplace of Buddha in the Indian sub-continent and returned to Chang'an (modern day Xi'an) with a set of Buddhist sutras. </Source><Target>他突破重重关隘，横渡渺无人烟的地区，直到印度次大陆的佛教发源地，然后带着一套佛教经典回到长安（现西安）。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793860</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>7</Serial><Id>1093266794053</Id><Source>The voluminous set of sutras was written in the extremely difficult Sanskrit language. </Source><Target>这套卷帙浩繁的佛经是用极难懂的梵语所著。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794053</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>8</Serial><Id>1093266794192</Id><Source>Together with his doyens of pupils, he completed the translation of some 75 volumes of the sutras into the equally difficult Chinese languages</Source><Target>他与他的高徒一起将 75 卷佛经翻译成同等难度的汉语。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794192</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>9</Serial><Id>1093266794333</Id><Source>The 10 Stages</Source><Target>10 个步骤</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794333</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>10</Serial><Id>1093266794352</Id><Source>Buddhist sutras translated into Chinese prior the Tang dynasty were difficult to comprehend because the first translators were Buddhist monks of non-Han Chinese origin. </Source><Target>唐朝以前，汉译佛经颇令人费解，因为最初的译者是非汉族血统的和尚。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794352</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>11</Serial><Id>1093266794516</Id><Source>It took China several hundred years to bring forth a selection of Buddhist monks who could master both the Sanskrit language as well as the complex Buddhism doctrines, which were written in Sanskrit. </Source><Target>几百年后，才出现了一批和尚，他们既精通梵文，又深晓复杂的梵经义理。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794516</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>12</Serial><Id>1093266794692</Id><Source>And Xuan Zang was recognized as foremost among them. </Source><Target>而玄奘被公认为是其中最卓越的大师。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794692</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>13</Serial><Id>1093266794763</Id><Source>He was appointed chief of the Tang dynasty imperial translation center. </Source><Target>他被指定为唐代官方译经院的负责人， </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794763</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>14</Serial><Id>1093266794853</Id><Source>It was he who designed and implemented a translation workflow that would guarantee the quality of the final product. </Source><Target>他设计并实施了一套翻译工作流程，以确保最后译作的质量。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794853</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>15</Serial><Id>1093266794974</Id><Source>The process detailed below is well worth adopting by any modern day translation team.</Source><Target>下面所列的详细步骤是值得让当今任何翻译队伍采纳借鉴的。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794974</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>16</Serial><Id>1093266795125</Id><Source>Stage 1</Source><Target>第一步</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795125</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>17</Serial><Id>1093266795138</Id><Source>Master translator and Buddhism expert to jointly study and interpret the original text written in Sanskrit. </Source><Target>由主译和佛教专家共同研讨梵经义理，并解释梵语经文。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795138</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>18</Serial><Id>1093266795269</Id><Source>It could involve one or more persons.</Source><Target>此过程需要一个或更多的人参与。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795269</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>19</Serial><Id>1093266795322</Id><Source>Stage 2</Source><Target>第二步</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795322</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>20</Serial><Id>1093266795337</Id><Source>All members of the translation team to attend a recital of the text in question by the Master translator. </Source><Target>翻译队伍的所有成员吟诵经文，由主译提问。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795337</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>21</Serial><Id>1093266795525</Id><Source>The purpose is to verify the accuracy of the interpretation undertaken in Stage 1. </Source><Target>其目的是检验第一步中解释的准确性。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795525</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>22</Serial><Id>1093266795617</Id><Source>A recital is necessary because the scriptures were originally written for recitation.</Source><Target>因为经文最初就是用于吟诵的，所以此过程尤显必要。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795617</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>23</Serial><Id>1093266795725</Id><Source>Stage 3</Source><Target>第三步</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795725</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>24</Serial><Id>1093266795739</Id><Source>A team of junior translators produces the first Chinese draft of the Sanskrit text. </Source><Target>由初级翻译人员第一次将梵语经文翻译成汉语初稿， </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795739</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>25</Serial><Id>1093266795838</Id><Source>The draft is a combination of transliteration of Sanskrit terms and standard Chinese.</Source><Target>该初稿包含梵文术语的音译和标准汉语。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795838</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>26</Serial><Id>1093266795952</Id><Source>Stage 4</Source><Target>第四步</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795952</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>27</Serial><Id>1093266796006</Id><Source>Production of a complete Chinese version by a senior native Chinese Buddhist monk trained to undertake scripture translation. </Source><Target>由一位母语为汉语的高僧负责将全部的汉语译文整理成经文。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796006</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>28</Serial><Id>1093266796174</Id><Source>This is the most important stage in the entire process and it must be undertaken by a monk with an in-depth knowledge of Chinese culture and language.</Source><Target>这是所有步骤中最重要的一步，必须由一位深晓中国文化和语言的佛教大师负责。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796174</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>29</Serial><Id>1093266796351</Id><Source>Stage 5</Source><Target>第五步</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796351</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>30</Serial><Id>1093266796367</Id><Source>Refinement of sentence structure of the complete Chinese version. </Source><Target>将最后中文译文的句子结构进行润色加工， </Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796367</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>31</Serial><Id>1093266796460</Id><Source>This is a necessary stage because of the vast linguistic differences between the source and target language.</Source><Target>这一步非常必要，因为在源语言与目标语言之间存在巨大的语言差异。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796460</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>32</Serial><Id>1093266796587</Id><Source>Stage 6</Source><Target>第六步</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796587</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>33</Serial><Id>1093266796604</Id><Source>Reverse translation of the Chinese version into Sanskrit in order to verify the accuracy of the interpretation of the original text. </Source><Target>为确保原文翻译的准确性，将中文译文翻回梵语。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796604</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>34</Serial><Id>1093266796755</Id><Source>Mistakes in interpretation are to be promptly rectified in the Chinese version.</Source><Target>翻译中的错误可以迅速地在译文中得以纠正。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796755</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>35</Serial><Id>1093266796864</Id><Source>Stage 7</Source><Target>第七步</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796864</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>36</Serial><Id>1093266796880</Id><Source>Review of the verified Chinese version to identify errors in character usage, and refinement of linguistic expressions to improve readability.</Source><Target>再次检查校验后的中文译文，找出措词不当处，将语言表达得更加明确精炼，提高其可读性。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796880</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>37</Serial><Id>1093266797078</Id><Source>Stage 8</Source><Target>第八步</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797078</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>38</Serial><Id>1093266797098</Id><Source>Further polishing to improve the literary beauty of the language and adding colors to the otherwise monotonous writings.</Source><Target>再次将译文进行润色，增强其语言的文学欣赏性，并对单调部分加以修饰。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797098</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>39</Serial><Id>1093266797242</Id><Source>Stage 9</Source><Target>第九步</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797242</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>40</Serial><Id>1093266797261</Id><Source>Verification of the audio quality by reciting the translation aloud. </Source><Target>通过大声朗读译文，确定译文的听觉质量。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797261</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>41</Serial><Id>1093266797353</Id><Source>The audio effect is important because scriptures are meant for preaching to an audience.</Source><Target>音效是很重要的，因为经文是用于讲述给听众的。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797353</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>42</Serial><Id>1093266797464</Id><Source>Stage 10</Source><Target>第十步</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797464</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>43</Serial><Id>1093266797482</Id><Source>Final check by the Master Translator.</Source><Target>由主译最后检查译文。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797482</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>44</Serial><Id>1093266797537</Id><Source>Conclusion</Source><Target>总结</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040705T121341Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797537</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>45</Serial><Id>1093266797565</Id><Source>Xuan Zang did a great job in the translation of the Buddhist sutras. </Source><Target>玄奘为佛经的翻译做出了巨大的贡献。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797565</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>46</Serial><Id>1093266797652</Id><Source>He was able to excel not only was he an outstanding linguist but also he was wholeheartedly committed to the task as a devoted Buddhist with an extraordinary understanding of its contents. </Source><Target>这不仅在于他是一个杰出的语言学家，而且他作为一个虔诚的佛教徒，凭着对佛经的超凡的理解力，将全身心投入到这项事业中。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101705Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797652</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>47</Serial><Id>1093266797842</Id><Source>Indeed, he dedicated thirteen years of his life to the task. </Source><Target>他为这项工程投入了十三年时间。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797842</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>48</Serial><Id>1093266797899</Id><Source>And the task was not simply transforming one language into another. </Source><Target>这已不仅仅是将一种语言翻译成另外一种语言。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797899</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>49</Serial><Id>1093266797991</Id><Source>In order to effectively spread Buddhism, the sutras in Chinese would have to be understood by the Chinese devotees. </Source><Target>为了有效地传播佛教，中文版的佛经必须被中国的信徒所读懂。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101717Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797991</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>50</Serial><Id>1093266798115</Id><Source>In other words, he had to take into account the marketplace. </Source><Target>换句话说，他必须考虑这个群体。</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798115</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>51</Serial><Id>1093266798174</Id><Source>Was it intended for the gentry for whom Buddhism depended for their financial support or was it for the less literate general populace to widen market share or was it for both?</Source><Target>是为那些为佛教提供财政支持的上层阶级服务，还是为那些没有太多文化修养的普通百姓服务，以扩展佛教的影响范围，或者两者兼顾？</Target><SourceLang>en</SourceLang><TargetLang>zh-cn</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101647Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798174</Prop></Pair>
