<Pair><Serial>38</Serial><Id>1093266797098</Id><Source>Nueva revisión para mejorar la belleza literaria de la lengua y dar un toque de color a los textos de lectura monótona.</Source><Target>Further polishing to improve the literary beauty of the language and adding colors to the otherwise monotonous writings.</Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797098</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>39</Serial><Id>1093266797242</Id><Source>Paso 9</Source><Target>Stage 9</Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797242</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>40</Serial><Id>1093266797261</Id><Source>Comprobación de la musicalidad del texto mediante lectura en voz alta de la traducción. </Source><Target>Verification of the audio quality by reciting the translation aloud. </Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797261</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>41</Serial><Id>1093266797353</Id><Source>El aspecto auditivo es importante, puesto que las oraciones serán recitadas en público.</Source><Target>The audio effect is important because scriptures are meant for preaching to an audience.</Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797353</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>42</Serial><Id>1093266797464</Id><Source>Paso 10</Source><Target>Stage 10</Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797464</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>43</Serial><Id>1093266797482</Id><Source>Revisión final por parte del traductor experto. </Source><Target>Final check by the Master Translator.</Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797482</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>44</Serial><Id>1093266797537</Id><Source>Conclusión</Source><Target>Conclusion</Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040705T121341Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797537</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>45</Serial><Id>1093266797565</Id><Source>Xuan Zang elaboró una traducción extraordinaria de los sutras budistas. </Source><Target>Xuan Zang did a great job in the translation of the Buddhist sutras. </Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797565</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>46</Serial><Id>1093266797652</Id><Source>Demostró que no sólo era un lingüista excepcional, sino también un budista devoto que se volcó en cuerpo y alma en un cometido que conocía a fondo. </Source><Target>He was able to excel not only was he an outstanding linguist but also he was wholeheartedly committed to the task as a devoted Buddhist with an extraordinary understanding of its contents. </Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101705Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797652</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>47</Serial><Id>1093266797842</Id><Source>Dedicó trece años a su gran obra, </Source><Target>Indeed, he dedicated thirteen years of his life to the task. </Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797842</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>48</Serial><Id>1093266797899</Id><Source>que no se limitaba a transformar una lengua en otra, </Source><Target>And the task was not simply transforming one language into another. </Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797899</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>49</Serial><Id>1093266797991</Id><Source>puesto que para difundir el budismo el único medio era que los devotos chinos comprendieran los sutras.</Source><Target>In order to effectively spread Buddhism, the sutras in Chinese would have to be understood by the Chinese devotees. </Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101717Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797991</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>50</Serial><Id>1093266798115</Id><Source>En otras palabras: debía tener en cuenta el mercado. </Source><Target>In other words, he had to take into account the marketplace. </Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798115</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>51</Serial><Id>1093266798174</Id><Source>¿Su esfuerzo iba dirigido a la elite, de cuyo apoyo económico dependía el budismo, o a un pueblo menos culto, lo que permitiría ampliar la cota de mercado? ¿O tal vez a ambos?</Source><Target>Was it intended for the gentry for whom Buddhism depended for their financial support or was it for the less literate general populace to widen market share or was it for both?</Target><SourceLang>es</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101647Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798174</Prop></Pair>
