<Asset package="..\..\Samples\XuanZang.tmx" original="it - en" source-lang="it" target-lang="en">
<Pair><Serial>1</Serial><Id>1093266792948</Id><Source>Xuan Zang, probabilmente il più grande traduttore cinese</Source><Target>Xuan Zang, Possibly China's Greatest Translator</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020919T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266792948</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>2</Serial><Id>1093266793131</Id><Source>Il suo metodo di controllo di qualità in 10 fasi risale a più di 1300 anni fa ed è molto più accurato e preciso di qualsiasi metodo attuale.</Source><Target>His 10-stage quality control process initiated more than 1300 years ago is far more thorough and exacting than any existing today.</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793131</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>3</Serial><Id>1093266793344</Id><Source>Introduzione</Source><Target>Introduction</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793344</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>4</Serial><Id>1093266793385</Id><Source>I Cinesi d'ogni età, in Cina e fuori di essa, conoscono la versione in cinese classico delle avventure di Xuan Zang, il pio monaco buddista della dinastia Tang e dei suoi tre leggendari discepoli, l'indistruttibile Re Scimmia, il Grande Saggio; il Porcello delle Otto Astinenze (del Buddismo) e Sabbioso, il terzo discepolo. </Source><Target>Every Chinese, young and old, within and outside China, knows the classical language rendering of the exploits of Xuan Zang, the pious Tang dynasty monk and his three storybook disciples, the indestructible Monkey King, the Great Sage; Brother Pig, the Eight Denials (of Buddhism) and Sand Monk, the third disciple. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793385</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>5</Serial><Id>1093266793776</Id><Source>Nella vita reale, Xuan Zang fu un monaco veramente eccezionale. </Source><Target>In real life, Xuan Zang was a truly remarkable Buddhist monk. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793776</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>6</Serial><Id>1093266793860</Id><Source>Egli attraversò zone ostili e inesplorate fino a raggiungere il luogo di nascita di Budda, nel subcontinente indiano. </Source><Target>He traveled on land on the way through hostile and uncharted territory to the birthplace of Buddha in the Indian sub-continent and returned to Chang'an (modern day Xi'an) with a set of Buddhist sutras. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793860</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>7</Serial><Id>1093266794053</Id><Source>Fece ritorno a Chang'an (l'attuale Xi'an) con una voluminosa edizione completa di sutra buddisti, scritti nel difficilissimo Sanscrito. </Source><Target>The voluminous set of sutras was written in the extremely difficult Sanskrit language. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794053</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>8</Serial><Id>1093266794192</Id><Source>In collaborazione con i suoi allievi più esperti, egli tradusse qualcosa come 75 volumi di sutra nelle altrettanto ostiche lingue cinesi. </Source><Target>Together with his doyens of pupils, he completed the translation of some 75 volumes of the sutras into the equally difficult Chinese languages</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794192</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>9</Serial><Id>1093266794333</Id><Source>Le 10 fasi</Source><Target>The 10 Stages</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794333</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>10</Serial><Id>1093266794352</Id><Source>Le traduzioni di sutra buddisti anteriori alla dinastia Tang erano di difficile comprensione, giacché i monaci che le avevano tradotte non erano di origine Han.</Source><Target>Buddhist sutras translated into Chinese prior the Tang dynasty were difficult to comprehend because the first translators were Buddhist monks of non-Han Chinese origin. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794352</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>11</Serial><Id>1093266794516</Id><Source>Ci vollero alcuni secoli prima che in Cina si formasse un gruppo di monaci buddisti in grado di dominare sia le complesse dottrine buddiste sia il sanscrito, lingua in cui queste furono scritte. </Source><Target>It took China several hundred years to bring forth a selection of Buddhist monks who could master both the Sanskrit language as well as the complex Buddhism doctrines, which were written in Sanskrit. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794516</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>12</Serial><Id>1093266794692</Id><Source>Xuan Zang, considerato il massimo rappresentante di questo gruppo, </Source><Target>And Xuan Zang was recognized as foremost among them. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794692</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>13</Serial><Id>1093266794763</Id><Source>fu nominato direttore del centro di traduzione della dinastia imperiale Tang.</Source><Target>He was appointed chief of the Tang dynasty imperial translation center. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794763</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>14</Serial><Id>1093266794853</Id><Source>Fu lui a creare e a mettere a punto un sistema di lavoro per garantire la qualità del prodotto finale.</Source><Target>It was he who designed and implemented a translation workflow that would guarantee the quality of the final product. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794853</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>15</Serial><Id>1093266794974</Id><Source>Anche ai giorni nostri, il metodo descritto qui sotto può benissimo essere adottato da qualsiasi equipe di traduttori.</Source><Target>The process detailed below is well worth adopting by any modern day translation team.</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794974</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>16</Serial><Id>1093266795125</Id><Source>Fase 1</Source><Target>Stage 1</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795125</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>17</Serial><Id>1093266795138</Id><Source>Il maestro traduttore e l'esperto di buddismo studiano e interpretano insieme il testo originale sanscrito. </Source><Target>Master translator and Buddhism expert to jointly study and interpret the original text written in Sanskrit. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795138</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>18</Serial><Id>1093266795269</Id><Source>A questa fase possono partecipare una o più persone.</Source><Target>It could involve one or more persons.</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795269</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>19</Serial><Id>1093266795322</Id><Source>Fase 2</Source><Target>Stage 2</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795322</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>20</Serial><Id>1093266795337</Id><Source>Tutti i membri del gruppo di traduzione assistono alla lettura del testo in questione da parte del maestro traduttore, </Source><Target>All members of the translation team to attend a recital of the text in question by the Master translator. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795337</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>21</Serial><Id>1093266795525</Id><Source>allo scopo di verificare l'esattezza di quanto interpretato nella fase 1.</Source><Target>The purpose is to verify the accuracy of the interpretation undertaken in Stage 1. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795525</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>22</Serial><Id>1093266795617</Id><Source>La lettura è necessaria perché originariamente il testo fu concepito per la recitazione.</Source><Target>A recital is necessary because the scriptures were originally written for recitation.</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795617</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>23</Serial><Id>1093266795725</Id><Source>Fase 3</Source><Target>Stage 3</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795725</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>24</Serial><Id>1093266795739</Id><Source>Un gruppo di allievi traduttori redige una prima bozza in cinese del testo sanscrito. </Source><Target>A team of junior translators produces the first Chinese draft of the Sanskrit text. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795739</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>25</Serial><Id>1093266795838</Id><Source>La bozza è una combinazione di traslitterazione di termini sanscriti e di termini in cinese standard.</Source><Target>The draft is a combination of transliteration of Sanskrit terms and standard Chinese.</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795838</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>26</Serial><Id>1093266795952</Id><Source>Fase 4</Source><Target>Stage 4</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795952</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>27</Serial><Id>1093266796006</Id><Source>Elaborazione di una versione cinese completa a cura un monaco buddista di madrelingua cinese, esperto e specializzato nella traduzione di testi sacri. </Source><Target>Production of a complete Chinese version by a senior native Chinese Buddhist monk trained to undertake scripture translation. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796006</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>28</Serial><Id>1093266796174</Id><Source>Questa è la fase più importante dell'intero processo e deve essere affidata a un monaco con una perfetta padronanza della cultura e della lingua cinese.</Source><Target>This is the most important stage in the entire process and it must be undertaken by a monk with an in-depth knowledge of Chinese culture and language.</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796174</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>29</Serial><Id>1093266796351</Id><Source>Fase 5</Source><Target>Stage 5</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796351</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>30</Serial><Id>1093266796367</Id><Source>Perfezionamento della struttura delle frasi dell'intera versione cinese. </Source><Target>Refinement of sentence structure of the complete Chinese version. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796367</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>31</Serial><Id>1093266796460</Id><Source>È una fase necessaria, viste le grandi differenze linguistiche tra la lingua di partenza e quella d'arrivo.</Source><Target>This is a necessary stage because of the vast linguistic differences between the source and target language.</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796460</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>32</Serial><Id>1093266796587</Id><Source>Fase 6</Source><Target>Stage 6</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796587</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>33</Serial><Id>1093266796604</Id><Source>Traduzione inversa della versione cinese al sanscrito, al fine di verificare l'esattezza dell'interpretazione del testo originale. </Source><Target>Reverse translation of the Chinese version into Sanskrit in order to verify the accuracy of the interpretation of the original text. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796604</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>34</Serial><Id>1093266796755</Id><Source>Errori d'interpretazione sono immediatamente rettificati nella versione cinese.</Source><Target>Mistakes in interpretation are to be promptly rectified in the Chinese version.</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796755</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>35</Serial><Id>1093266796864</Id><Source>Fase 7</Source><Target>Stage 7</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796864</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>36</Serial><Id>1093266796880</Id><Source>Revisione della versione cinese precedentemente controllata, al fine di individuare errori nell'uso di caratteri. Perfezionamento delle espressioni idiomatiche per una migliore leggibilità.</Source><Target>Review of the verified Chinese version to identify errors in character usage, and refinement of linguistic expressions to improve readability.</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796880</Prop></Pair>
