<Pair><Serial>40</Serial><Id>1093266797261</Id><Source>Lettura ad alta voce della traduzione per verificarne la qualità acustica; </Source><Target>Verification of the audio quality by reciting the translation aloud. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797261</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>41</Serial><Id>1093266797353</Id><Source>di grande importanza, considerato che le scritture furono concepite per essere recitate in pubblico.</Source><Target>The audio effect is important because scriptures are meant for preaching to an audience.</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797353</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>42</Serial><Id>1093266797464</Id><Source>Fase 10</Source><Target>Stage 10</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797464</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>43</Serial><Id>1093266797482</Id><Source>Verifica finale da parte del maestro traduttore.</Source><Target>Final check by the Master Translator.</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797482</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>44</Serial><Id>1093266797537</Id><Source>Conclusione</Source><Target>Conclusion</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040705T121341Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797537</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>45</Serial><Id>1093266797565</Id><Source>Xuan Zang fece un'eccezionale traduzione dei sutra buddisti. </Source><Target>Xuan Zang did a great job in the translation of the Buddhist sutras. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797565</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>46</Serial><Id>1093266797652</Id><Source>Personaggio fuori del comune, egli non solo fu uno straordinario linguista, ma anche un buddista devoto, che si dedicò con abnegazione a una materia che conosceva a fondo: impegnò, </Source><Target>He was able to excel not only was he an outstanding linguist but also he was wholeheartedly committed to the task as a devoted Buddhist with an extraordinary understanding of its contents. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101705Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797652</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>47</Serial><Id>1093266797842</Id><Source>infatti, ben tredici anni in quest'impresa.</Source><Target>Indeed, he dedicated thirteen years of his life to the task. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797842</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>48</Serial><Id>1093266797899</Id><Source>E non si trattava solo di trasformare una lingua in un'altra: per un'efficace divulgazione del Buddismo, </Source><Target>And the task was not simply transforming one language into another. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797899</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>49</Serial><Id>1093266797991</Id><Source>i sutra in cinese dovevano risultare comprensibili ai fedeli cinesi.</Source><Target>In order to effectively spread Buddhism, the sutras in Chinese would have to be understood by the Chinese devotees. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101717Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797991</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>50</Serial><Id>1093266798115</Id><Source>In altre parole, bisognava tener conto del mercato. </Source><Target>In other words, he had to take into account the marketplace. </Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798115</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>51</Serial><Id>1093266798174</Id><Source>A chi era destinata la traduzione? All'elite dal cui appoggio dipendevano gli interessi del Buddismo, al popolino, allo scopo di incrementare la quota di mercato, oppure ad entrambi?</Source><Target>Was it intended for the gentry for whom Buddhism depended for their financial support or was it for the less literate general populace to widen market share or was it for both?</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101647Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798174</Prop></Pair>
