<Pair><Serial>43</Serial><Id>1093266797482</Id><Source>Verifica finale da parte del maestro traduttore.</Source><Target>번역 팀장이 최종 점검한다.</Target><SourceLang>it</SourceLang><TargetLang>ko</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797482</Prop></Pair>
