<Pair><Serial>1</Serial><Id>1093266792948</Id><Source>현장법사(玄奬法師), 중국 최고의 번역가</Source><Target>Xuan Zang - möglicherweise Chinas größter Übersetzer</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020919T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266792948</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>2</Serial><Id>1093266793131</Id><Source>그가 1300여년 전 시작한 10단계 품질 관리 방법은 현존하는 것보다 훨씬 더 철저하고 정확하다.</Source><Target>Das von ihm entwickelte zehnstufige Qualitätssicherungsverfahren ist über 1300 Jahre alt, jedoch erheblich gründlicher und genauer als die heutigen Verfahren.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793131</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>3</Serial><Id>1093266793344</Id><Source>서론</Source><Target>Einführung</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793344</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>4</Serial><Id>1093266793385</Id><Source>중국 국내외, 남녀노소를 불문한 모든 중국인들은 당대(唐代, 618-907 AD)의 독실한 승려인 현장법사와 그의 이야기책 속에 나오는 세 명의 제자들, 즉 공(空)을 깨닫는다라는 뜻을 지닌 불멸의 손오공, (불교의) 여덟 가지 계율을 나타내는 저팔계, 세 번째 제자인 사오정이 이루어낸 업적 가운데 고전적인 언어 번역에 대해서 알고 있다.</Source><Target>Jeder Chinese, ob alt oder jung, innerhalb oder außerhalb Chinas, kennt die Heldentaten der klassischen Sprachübertragung Xuan Zangs, des frommen Mönchs der Tang-Dynastie, und seiner drei sagenhaften Schüler, des unsterblichen Affenkönigs, des Großen Weisen; Schweinekopfs, der Acht Verneinungen des Buddhismus und Bruder Sands, des dritten Schülers. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793385</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>5</Serial><Id>1093266793776</Id><Source>실제로 현장법사는 매우 뛰어난 불교 승려였다.</Source><Target>Zu Lebzeiten war Xuan Zang ein wahrhaftig außergewöhnlicher buddhistischer Mönch. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793776</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>6</Serial><Id>1093266793860</Id><Source>인도 아대륙(亞大陸)에 있는 부처의 탄생지를 찾기 위해 적대적이고 지도에도 나타나있지 않은 지역들을 거쳐 대륙을 여행했고 일련의 불교 경전을 가지고 장안(현재의 시안(서안, 西安))으로 돌아왔다.</Source><Target>Er reiste durch das Land durch feindliche und unerforschte Gebiete zum Geburtsort Buddhas auf dem indischen Subkontinent und kehrte mit einer Vielzahl buddhistischer Sutras nach Chang'an (dem heutigen Xi'an) zurück. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793860</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>7</Serial><Id>1093266794053</Id><Source>방대한 양의 경전은 극도로 어려운 산스크리트어(범어, 梵語)로 저술되어 있었다.</Source><Target>Die umfangreiche Reihe an Sutras war im äußerst komplizierten Sanskrit verfasst. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794053</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>8</Serial><Id>1093266794192</Id><Source>그는 오랫동안 수행해온 제자들과 함께 75권이나 되는 경전을 산스크리트어만큼 어려운 중국어로 번역했다.</Source><Target>Gemeinsam mit seinen erfahrensten Schülern übersetzte er die annähernd 75 Sutra-Bände in die gleichermaßen schwierigen chinesischen Sprachen.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794192</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>9</Serial><Id>1093266794333</Id><Source>열 단계</Source><Target>Die 10 Stufen</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794333</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>10</Serial><Id>1093266794352</Id><Source>당대 이전에 중국어로 번역된 불교 경전들은 한족(漢族) 출신이 아닌 불교 승려들이 최초로 번역했기 때문에 이해하기 어려웠다.</Source><Target>Buddhistische Sutras, die vor der Tang-Dynastie ins Chinesische übertragen worden waren, waren nur schwer verständlich, da die ersten Übersetzer buddhistische Mönche nicht-hanchinesischer Herkunft waren. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794352</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>11</Serial><Id>1093266794516</Id><Source>중국은 산스크리트어 뿐만 아니라 산스크리트어로 쓰여진 복잡한 불교의 교리에 정통한 불교 승려들을 배출하는데 수 백년이 걸렸다.</Source><Target>Es sollten mehrere hundert Jahre vergehen, ehe China mehrere buddhistischer Mönche hervorbrachte, die sowohl Sanskrit als auch die komplizierten buddhistischen Lehren beherrschten, die auf Sanskrit geschrieben waren. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794516</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>12</Serial><Id>1093266794692</Id><Source>현장법사는 그들 가운데에서도 최고로 인정 받았다.</Source><Target>Unter ihnen galt Xuan Zang als einer der führenden und begabtesten Schüler. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794692</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>13</Serial><Id>1093266794763</Id><Source>그는 당대 황실 번역소(역경원)의 대표자로 임명되었다.</Source><Target>Er wurde zum Leiter des kaiserlichen Übersetzungszentrums der Tang-Dynastie ernannt. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794763</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>14</Serial><Id>1093266794853</Id><Source>최종 완성본의 품질을 보증할 수 있는 번역 작업 과정을 고안해내고 실행한 사람이 바로 그였다.</Source><Target>Er entwickelte und führte einen Übersetzungsablauf ein, mit dem die Qualität des Endprodukts garantiert wurde. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794853</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>15</Serial><Id>1093266794974</Id><Source>아래 열거한 과정은 오늘날의 번역 팀도 도입해 볼 만한 가치가 있을 것이다.</Source><Target>Das im Folgenden aufgeschlüsselte Verfahren ist es wert, von modernen Übersetzungsteams aufgegriffen zu werden.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794974</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>16</Serial><Id>1093266795125</Id><Source>1 단계</Source><Target>Stufe 1</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795125</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>17</Serial><Id>1093266795138</Id><Source>번역 팀장과 불교 전문가가 함께 산스크리트어로 쓰여진 원문을 연구하고 해석한다.</Source><Target>Chefübersetzer und Buddhismusexperten studieren und legen gemeinsam den Originaltext in Sanskrit aus. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795138</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>18</Serial><Id>1093266795269</Id><Source>여기에는 한 명 이상의 사람들이 참여할 것이다.</Source><Target>Das können eine oder mehrere Personen sein.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795269</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>19</Serial><Id>1093266795322</Id><Source>2 단계</Source><Target>Stufe 2</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795322</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>20</Serial><Id>1093266795337</Id><Source>번역 팀의 모든 멤버들이 번역 팀장이 문제를 제기한 본문의 낭독에 참여한다.</Source><Target>Alle Mitarbeiter des Übersetzungsteams wohnen der Lesung des betreffenden Textes durch den Chefübersetzer bei. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795337</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>21</Serial><Id>1093266795525</Id><Source>1단계에서 수행한 해석이 정확한지 확인하는 것이 목적이다.</Source><Target>Dies dient der Sicherung der Genauigkeit der in Stufe 1 gewonnenen Auslegung. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795525</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>22</Serial><Id>1093266795617</Id><Source>경전들은 원래 낭독하기 위해 쓴 것이기 때문에 낭독이 필수적이다.</Source><Target>Der Vortrag des Textes ist notwendig, da die Schriften ursprünglich zum Vorlesen gedacht waren.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795617</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>23</Serial><Id>1093266795725</Id><Source>3 단계</Source><Target>Stufe 3</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795725</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>24</Serial><Id>1093266795739</Id><Source>하위 번역팀이 산스크리트어 본문에 대해 중국어 초안을 만든다.</Source><Target>Ein Team von Übersetzern erstellt den ersten chinesischen Entwurf des Sanskrit-Textes. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795739</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>25</Serial><Id>1093266795838</Id><Source>이 초안에는 산스크리트 용어의 음역(音譯)과 중국 표준어가 결합되어 있다.</Source><Target>Der Entwurf enthält eine Mischung an transliterierten Sanskrit-Begriffen und Standardchinesisch.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795838</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>26</Serial><Id>1093266795952</Id><Source>4 단계</Source><Target>Stufe 4</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795952</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>27</Serial><Id>1093266796006</Id><Source>토종 중국인으로 경전 번역에 숙련된 중견 불교 승려에 의한 완전한 중국어판을  작성한다.</Source><Target>Erarbeitung einer vollständig chinesischen Version durch einen erfahrenen buddhistischen Mönch, dessen Muttersprache Chinesisch ist und der in der Übersetzung heiliger Schriften geschult ist. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796006</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>28</Serial><Id>1093266796174</Id><Source>전 과정 중에서 이 단계가 가장 중요하며 중국의 문화와 언어에 대해 심층적인 지식을 가지고 있는 승려가 수행해야만 한다.</Source><Target>Dies ist die wichtigste Stufe des gesamten Verfahrens. Diese Aufgabe obliegt einem Mönch, der über umfangreiche und tiefgreifende Kenntnisse der chinesischen Kultur und Sprache verfügt.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796174</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>29</Serial><Id>1093266796351</Id><Source>5 단계</Source><Target>Stufe 5</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796351</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>30</Serial><Id>1093266796367</Id><Source>완전한 중국어 판의 문장 구조를 다듬는다.</Source><Target>Ausarbeitung der Satzstruktur der vollständigen chinesischen Version. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796367</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>31</Serial><Id>1093266796460</Id><Source>이 단계는 원문과 목표 언어 사이에 커다란 언어적 차이가 있기 때문에 필수적이다.</Source><Target>Die Notwendigkeit dieser Stufe ergibt sich aus den immensen sprachlichen Unterschieden zwischen Ursprungs- und Zielsprache.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796460</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>32</Serial><Id>1093266796587</Id><Source>6 단계</Source><Target>Stufe 6</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796587</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>33</Serial><Id>1093266796604</Id><Source>원문의 해석이 정확한지 검증하기 위해 중국어 판을 산스크리트어로 거꾸로 번역한다.</Source><Target>Übersetzung der chinesischen Version in Sanskrit, um die Genauigkeit der Übertragung des Ursprungstextes zu überprüfen. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796604</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>34</Serial><Id>1093266796755</Id><Source>해석상의 실수를 중국어 판에서 신속하게 수정할 수 있다.</Source><Target>Fehler in der Übertragung müssen in der chinesischen Version unverzüglich berichtigt werden.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796755</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>35</Serial><Id>1093266796864</Id><Source>7 단계</Source><Target>Stufe 7</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796864</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>36</Serial><Id>1093266796880</Id><Source>문자 사용 상의 오류를 찾아내기 위해 검증된 중국어 판을 재검토하고, 보다 읽기 쉽게 하기 위해 언어적 표현을 다듬는다.</Source><Target>Nachbearbeitung der überprüften chinesischen Version zur Ermittlung falsch verwendeter Zeichen, zur Verfeinerung des sprachlichen Ausdrucks und damit zur Verbesserung der Lesbarkeit.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796880</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>37</Serial><Id>1093266797078</Id><Source>8 단계</Source><Target>Stufe 8</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797078</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>38</Serial><Id>1093266797098</Id><Source>언어가 갖는 문학적 아름다움을 높이기 위해 세련되게 다듬기와 단조로운 문장들에 색채를 입힌다.</Source><Target>Letzter Schliff, um die literarische Schönheit der Sprache zu verbessern und um ansonsten eintönigen Schriften Farbigkeit zu geben.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797098</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>39</Serial><Id>1093266797242</Id><Source>9 단계</Source><Target>Stufe 9</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797242</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>40</Serial><Id>1093266797261</Id><Source>번역물을 큰소리로 낭독하여 음질을 확인한다. </Source><Target>Überprüfung der Klanggefälligkeit durch eine Lesung der Übersetzung. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797261</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>41</Serial><Id>1093266797353</Id><Source>경전은 청중을 설득하기 위한 것이므로 청각적인 효과가 중요하다.</Source><Target>Die akustische Wirkung ist wichtig, da die Schriften zur Predigt vor einer Zuhörerschaft vorgesehen sind.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797353</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>42</Serial><Id>1093266797464</Id><Source>10 단계</Source><Target>Stufe 10</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797464</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>43</Serial><Id>1093266797482</Id><Source>번역 팀장이 최종 점검한다.</Source><Target>Letzte Prüfung durch den Chefübersetzer.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797482</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>44</Serial><Id>1093266797537</Id><Source>결론</Source><Target>Schlussbemerkung</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040705T121341Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797537</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>45</Serial><Id>1093266797565</Id><Source>현장법사는 불교 경전 번역에서 대단한 위업을 달성했다.</Source><Target>Xuan Zang hat für die Übersetzung der buddhistischen Sutras Bedeutendes geleistet. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797565</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>46</Serial><Id>1093266797652</Id><Source>그는 뛰어난 언어학자였을 뿐만 아니라, 귀의한 불자로서 경전 내용을 정확히 파악하여 전심 전력을 다해 과업을 수행한 뛰어난 사람이었다.</Source><Target>Er tat sich nicht nur als außergewöhnlicher Linguist hervor, sondern widmete sich auch als ergebener Buddhist mit einem überragenden inhaltlichen Verständnis dieser Aufgabe von ganzem Herzen. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101705Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797652</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>47</Serial><Id>1093266797842</Id><Source>실제로 그는 이 작업에 13년이라는 세월을 바쳤다.</Source><Target>Er hat dieser Arbeit dreizehn Jahre seines Lebens gewidmet. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797842</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>48</Serial><Id>1093266797899</Id><Source>그리고 이 작업은 단순히 하나의 언어를 다른 언어로 바꾸는 것이 아니었다.</Source><Target>Und die Aufgabe bestand nicht lediglich darin, eine Sprache in eine andere zu übertragen. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797899</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>49</Serial><Id>1093266797991</Id><Source>불교를 효과적으로 전파하기 위해서 중국어 경전을 중국인 신자들이 이해해야만 했다. </Source><Target>Um den Buddhismus wirkungsvoll zu verbreiten, mussten die chinesischsprachigen Sutras von den chinesischen Gläubigen wirklich verstanden werden. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101717Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797991</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>50</Serial><Id>1093266798115</Id><Source>다시 말해, 그는 속세를 염두에 두어야만 했다. </Source><Target>Mit anderen Worten, er musste den Absatzmarkt in Betracht ziehen: </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798115</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>51</Serial><Id>1093266798174</Id><Source>불교의 재정적인 지원을 맡았던 상류층을 향한 의도였는지, 아니면 불교 전파를 위해 덜 교육 받은 일반 서민들을 향한 의도였는지, 그도 아니면 그 모두를 위한 의도였는지에 대한 의문은 남는다.</Source><Target>Waren die Übersetzungen für den Adel gedacht, von dessen finanzieller Unterstützung der Buddhismus abhängig war, oder für die weniger gebildete breite Bevölkerung, um den Marktanteil zu erhöhen? Oder für beide?</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101647Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798174</Prop></Pair>
</Asset>
<Asset package="..\..\Samples\XuanZang.tmx" original="ko - en" source-lang="ko" target-lang="en">
<Pair><Serial>1</Serial><Id>1093266792948</Id><Source>현장법사(玄奬法師), 중국 최고의 번역가</Source><Target>Xuan Zang, Possibly China's Greatest Translator</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020919T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266792948</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>2</Serial><Id>1093266793131</Id><Source>그가 1300여년 전 시작한 10단계 품질 관리 방법은 현존하는 것보다 훨씬 더 철저하고 정확하다.</Source><Target>His 10-stage quality control process initiated more than 1300 years ago is far more thorough and exacting than any existing today.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793131</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>3</Serial><Id>1093266793344</Id><Source>서론</Source><Target>Introduction</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793344</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>4</Serial><Id>1093266793385</Id><Source>중국 국내외, 남녀노소를 불문한 모든 중국인들은 당대(唐代, 618-907 AD)의 독실한 승려인 현장법사와 그의 이야기책 속에 나오는 세 명의 제자들, 즉 공(空)을 깨닫는다라는 뜻을 지닌 불멸의 손오공, (불교의) 여덟 가지 계율을 나타내는 저팔계, 세 번째 제자인 사오정이 이루어낸 업적 가운데 고전적인 언어 번역에 대해서 알고 있다.</Source><Target>Every Chinese, young and old, within and outside China, knows the classical language rendering of the exploits of Xuan Zang, the pious Tang dynasty monk and his three storybook disciples, the indestructible Monkey King, the Great Sage; Brother Pig, the Eight Denials (of Buddhism) and Sand Monk, the third disciple. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793385</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>5</Serial><Id>1093266793776</Id><Source>실제로 현장법사는 매우 뛰어난 불교 승려였다.</Source><Target>In real life, Xuan Zang was a truly remarkable Buddhist monk. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793776</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>6</Serial><Id>1093266793860</Id><Source>인도 아대륙(亞大陸)에 있는 부처의 탄생지를 찾기 위해 적대적이고 지도에도 나타나있지 않은 지역들을 거쳐 대륙을 여행했고 일련의 불교 경전을 가지고 장안(현재의 시안(서안, 西安))으로 돌아왔다.</Source><Target>He traveled on land on the way through hostile and uncharted territory to the birthplace of Buddha in the Indian sub-continent and returned to Chang'an (modern day Xi'an) with a set of Buddhist sutras. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793860</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>7</Serial><Id>1093266794053</Id><Source>방대한 양의 경전은 극도로 어려운 산스크리트어(범어, 梵語)로 저술되어 있었다.</Source><Target>The voluminous set of sutras was written in the extremely difficult Sanskrit language. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794053</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>8</Serial><Id>1093266794192</Id><Source>그는 오랫동안 수행해온 제자들과 함께 75권이나 되는 경전을 산스크리트어만큼 어려운 중국어로 번역했다.</Source><Target>Together with his doyens of pupils, he completed the translation of some 75 volumes of the sutras into the equally difficult Chinese languages</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794192</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>9</Serial><Id>1093266794333</Id><Source>열 단계</Source><Target>The 10 Stages</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794333</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>10</Serial><Id>1093266794352</Id><Source>당대 이전에 중국어로 번역된 불교 경전들은 한족(漢族) 출신이 아닌 불교 승려들이 최초로 번역했기 때문에 이해하기 어려웠다.</Source><Target>Buddhist sutras translated into Chinese prior the Tang dynasty were difficult to comprehend because the first translators were Buddhist monks of non-Han Chinese origin. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794352</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>11</Serial><Id>1093266794516</Id><Source>중국은 산스크리트어 뿐만 아니라 산스크리트어로 쓰여진 복잡한 불교의 교리에 정통한 불교 승려들을 배출하는데 수 백년이 걸렸다.</Source><Target>It took China several hundred years to bring forth a selection of Buddhist monks who could master both the Sanskrit language as well as the complex Buddhism doctrines, which were written in Sanskrit. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794516</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>12</Serial><Id>1093266794692</Id><Source>현장법사는 그들 가운데에서도 최고로 인정 받았다.</Source><Target>And Xuan Zang was recognized as foremost among them. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794692</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>13</Serial><Id>1093266794763</Id><Source>그는 당대 황실 번역소(역경원)의 대표자로 임명되었다.</Source><Target>He was appointed chief of the Tang dynasty imperial translation center. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794763</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>14</Serial><Id>1093266794853</Id><Source>최종 완성본의 품질을 보증할 수 있는 번역 작업 과정을 고안해내고 실행한 사람이 바로 그였다.</Source><Target>It was he who designed and implemented a translation workflow that would guarantee the quality of the final product. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794853</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>15</Serial><Id>1093266794974</Id><Source>아래 열거한 과정은 오늘날의 번역 팀도 도입해 볼 만한 가치가 있을 것이다.</Source><Target>The process detailed below is well worth adopting by any modern day translation team.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794974</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>16</Serial><Id>1093266795125</Id><Source>1 단계</Source><Target>Stage 1</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795125</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>17</Serial><Id>1093266795138</Id><Source>번역 팀장과 불교 전문가가 함께 산스크리트어로 쓰여진 원문을 연구하고 해석한다.</Source><Target>Master translator and Buddhism expert to jointly study and interpret the original text written in Sanskrit. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795138</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>18</Serial><Id>1093266795269</Id><Source>여기에는 한 명 이상의 사람들이 참여할 것이다.</Source><Target>It could involve one or more persons.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795269</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>19</Serial><Id>1093266795322</Id><Source>2 단계</Source><Target>Stage 2</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795322</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>20</Serial><Id>1093266795337</Id><Source>번역 팀의 모든 멤버들이 번역 팀장이 문제를 제기한 본문의 낭독에 참여한다.</Source><Target>All members of the translation team to attend a recital of the text in question by the Master translator. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795337</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>21</Serial><Id>1093266795525</Id><Source>1단계에서 수행한 해석이 정확한지 확인하는 것이 목적이다.</Source><Target>The purpose is to verify the accuracy of the interpretation undertaken in Stage 1. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795525</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>22</Serial><Id>1093266795617</Id><Source>경전들은 원래 낭독하기 위해 쓴 것이기 때문에 낭독이 필수적이다.</Source><Target>A recital is necessary because the scriptures were originally written for recitation.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795617</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>23</Serial><Id>1093266795725</Id><Source>3 단계</Source><Target>Stage 3</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795725</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>24</Serial><Id>1093266795739</Id><Source>하위 번역팀이 산스크리트어 본문에 대해 중국어 초안을 만든다.</Source><Target>A team of junior translators produces the first Chinese draft of the Sanskrit text. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795739</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>25</Serial><Id>1093266795838</Id><Source>이 초안에는 산스크리트 용어의 음역(音譯)과 중국 표준어가 결합되어 있다.</Source><Target>The draft is a combination of transliteration of Sanskrit terms and standard Chinese.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795838</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>26</Serial><Id>1093266795952</Id><Source>4 단계</Source><Target>Stage 4</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795952</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>27</Serial><Id>1093266796006</Id><Source>토종 중국인으로 경전 번역에 숙련된 중견 불교 승려에 의한 완전한 중국어판을  작성한다.</Source><Target>Production of a complete Chinese version by a senior native Chinese Buddhist monk trained to undertake scripture translation. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796006</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>28</Serial><Id>1093266796174</Id><Source>전 과정 중에서 이 단계가 가장 중요하며 중국의 문화와 언어에 대해 심층적인 지식을 가지고 있는 승려가 수행해야만 한다.</Source><Target>This is the most important stage in the entire process and it must be undertaken by a monk with an in-depth knowledge of Chinese culture and language.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796174</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>29</Serial><Id>1093266796351</Id><Source>5 단계</Source><Target>Stage 5</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796351</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>30</Serial><Id>1093266796367</Id><Source>완전한 중국어 판의 문장 구조를 다듬는다.</Source><Target>Refinement of sentence structure of the complete Chinese version. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796367</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>31</Serial><Id>1093266796460</Id><Source>이 단계는 원문과 목표 언어 사이에 커다란 언어적 차이가 있기 때문에 필수적이다.</Source><Target>This is a necessary stage because of the vast linguistic differences between the source and target language.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796460</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>32</Serial><Id>1093266796587</Id><Source>6 단계</Source><Target>Stage 6</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796587</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>33</Serial><Id>1093266796604</Id><Source>원문의 해석이 정확한지 검증하기 위해 중국어 판을 산스크리트어로 거꾸로 번역한다.</Source><Target>Reverse translation of the Chinese version into Sanskrit in order to verify the accuracy of the interpretation of the original text. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796604</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>34</Serial><Id>1093266796755</Id><Source>해석상의 실수를 중국어 판에서 신속하게 수정할 수 있다.</Source><Target>Mistakes in interpretation are to be promptly rectified in the Chinese version.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796755</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>35</Serial><Id>1093266796864</Id><Source>7 단계</Source><Target>Stage 7</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796864</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>36</Serial><Id>1093266796880</Id><Source>문자 사용 상의 오류를 찾아내기 위해 검증된 중국어 판을 재검토하고, 보다 읽기 쉽게 하기 위해 언어적 표현을 다듬는다.</Source><Target>Review of the verified Chinese version to identify errors in character usage, and refinement of linguistic expressions to improve readability.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796880</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>37</Serial><Id>1093266797078</Id><Source>8 단계</Source><Target>Stage 8</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797078</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>38</Serial><Id>1093266797098</Id><Source>언어가 갖는 문학적 아름다움을 높이기 위해 세련되게 다듬기와 단조로운 문장들에 색채를 입힌다.</Source><Target>Further polishing to improve the literary beauty of the language and adding colors to the otherwise monotonous writings.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797098</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>39</Serial><Id>1093266797242</Id><Source>9 단계</Source><Target>Stage 9</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797242</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>40</Serial><Id>1093266797261</Id><Source>번역물을 큰소리로 낭독하여 음질을 확인한다. </Source><Target>Verification of the audio quality by reciting the translation aloud. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797261</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>41</Serial><Id>1093266797353</Id><Source>경전은 청중을 설득하기 위한 것이므로 청각적인 효과가 중요하다.</Source><Target>The audio effect is important because scriptures are meant for preaching to an audience.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797353</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>42</Serial><Id>1093266797464</Id><Source>10 단계</Source><Target>Stage 10</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797464</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>43</Serial><Id>1093266797482</Id><Source>번역 팀장이 최종 점검한다.</Source><Target>Final check by the Master Translator.</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797482</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>44</Serial><Id>1093266797537</Id><Source>결론</Source><Target>Conclusion</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040705T121341Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797537</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>45</Serial><Id>1093266797565</Id><Source>현장법사는 불교 경전 번역에서 대단한 위업을 달성했다.</Source><Target>Xuan Zang did a great job in the translation of the Buddhist sutras. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797565</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>46</Serial><Id>1093266797652</Id><Source>그는 뛰어난 언어학자였을 뿐만 아니라, 귀의한 불자로서 경전 내용을 정확히 파악하여 전심 전력을 다해 과업을 수행한 뛰어난 사람이었다.</Source><Target>He was able to excel not only was he an outstanding linguist but also he was wholeheartedly committed to the task as a devoted Buddhist with an extraordinary understanding of its contents. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101705Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797652</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>47</Serial><Id>1093266797842</Id><Source>실제로 그는 이 작업에 13년이라는 세월을 바쳤다.</Source><Target>Indeed, he dedicated thirteen years of his life to the task. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797842</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>48</Serial><Id>1093266797899</Id><Source>그리고 이 작업은 단순히 하나의 언어를 다른 언어로 바꾸는 것이 아니었다.</Source><Target>And the task was not simply transforming one language into another. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797899</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>49</Serial><Id>1093266797991</Id><Source>불교를 효과적으로 전파하기 위해서 중국어 경전을 중국인 신자들이 이해해야만 했다. </Source><Target>In order to effectively spread Buddhism, the sutras in Chinese would have to be understood by the Chinese devotees. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101717Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797991</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>50</Serial><Id>1093266798115</Id><Source>다시 말해, 그는 속세를 염두에 두어야만 했다. </Source><Target>In other words, he had to take into account the marketplace. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798115</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>51</Serial><Id>1093266798174</Id><Source>불교의 재정적인 지원을 맡았던 상류층을 향한 의도였는지, 아니면 불교 전파를 위해 덜 교육 받은 일반 서민들을 향한 의도였는지, 그도 아니면 그 모두를 위한 의도였는지에 대한 의문은 남는다.</Source><Target>Was it intended for the gentry for whom Buddhism depended for their financial support or was it for the less literate general populace to widen market share or was it for both?</Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101647Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798174</Prop></Pair>
