<Pair><Serial>43</Serial><Id>1093266797482</Id><Source>번역 팀장이 최종 점검한다.</Source><Target>Revisión final por parte del traductor experto. </Target><SourceLang>ko</SourceLang><TargetLang>es</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797482</Prop></Pair>
