<Pair><Serial>1</Serial><Id>1093266792948</Id><Source>玄奘，中国最伟大的翻译家</Source><Target>Xuan Zang - möglicherweise Chinas größter Übersetzer</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020919T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266792948</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>2</Serial><Id>1093266793131</Id><Source>1300 多年前，他创立了翻译质量控制的十个步骤，其严谨与精确程度远远超过当今翻译界。</Source><Target>Das von ihm entwickelte zehnstufige Qualitätssicherungsverfahren ist über 1300 Jahre alt, jedoch erheblich gründlicher und genauer als die heutigen Verfahren.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793131</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>3</Serial><Id>1093266793344</Id><Source>简介</Source><Target>Einführung</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793344</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>4</Serial><Id>1093266793385</Id><Source>古今中外，几乎无人不晓唐代高僧玄奘在古代汉语方面所做的贡献，以及他在小说《西游记》中的三位徒弟，大徒弟孙悟空，二徒弟猪八戒和三徒弟沙僧。</Source><Target>Jeder Chinese, ob alt oder jung, innerhalb oder außerhalb Chinas, kennt die Heldentaten der klassischen Sprachübertragung Xuan Zangs, des frommen Mönchs der Tang-Dynastie, und seiner drei sagenhaften Schüler, des unsterblichen Affenkönigs, des Großen Weisen; Schweinekopfs, der Acht Verneinungen des Buddhismus und Bruder Sands, des dritten Schülers. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793385</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>5</Serial><Id>1093266793776</Id><Source>在真实生活中，玄奘的确是一个了不起的僧人。</Source><Target>Zu Lebzeiten war Xuan Zang ein wahrhaftig außergewöhnlicher buddhistischer Mönch. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793776</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>6</Serial><Id>1093266793860</Id><Source>他突破重重关隘，横渡渺无人烟的地区，直到印度次大陆的佛教发源地，然后带着一套佛教经典回到长安（现西安）。</Source><Target>Er reiste durch das Land durch feindliche und unerforschte Gebiete zum Geburtsort Buddhas auf dem indischen Subkontinent und kehrte mit einer Vielzahl buddhistischer Sutras nach Chang'an (dem heutigen Xi'an) zurück. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793860</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>7</Serial><Id>1093266794053</Id><Source>这套卷帙浩繁的佛经是用极难懂的梵语所著。</Source><Target>Die umfangreiche Reihe an Sutras war im äußerst komplizierten Sanskrit verfasst. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794053</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>8</Serial><Id>1093266794192</Id><Source>他与他的高徒一起将 75 卷佛经翻译成同等难度的汉语。</Source><Target>Gemeinsam mit seinen erfahrensten Schülern übersetzte er die annähernd 75 Sutra-Bände in die gleichermaßen schwierigen chinesischen Sprachen.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794192</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>9</Serial><Id>1093266794333</Id><Source>10 个步骤</Source><Target>Die 10 Stufen</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794333</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>10</Serial><Id>1093266794352</Id><Source>唐朝以前，汉译佛经颇令人费解，因为最初的译者是非汉族血统的和尚。</Source><Target>Buddhistische Sutras, die vor der Tang-Dynastie ins Chinesische übertragen worden waren, waren nur schwer verständlich, da die ersten Übersetzer buddhistische Mönche nicht-hanchinesischer Herkunft waren. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794352</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>11</Serial><Id>1093266794516</Id><Source>几百年后，才出现了一批和尚，他们既精通梵文，又深晓复杂的梵经义理。</Source><Target>Es sollten mehrere hundert Jahre vergehen, ehe China mehrere buddhistischer Mönche hervorbrachte, die sowohl Sanskrit als auch die komplizierten buddhistischen Lehren beherrschten, die auf Sanskrit geschrieben waren. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794516</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>12</Serial><Id>1093266794692</Id><Source>而玄奘被公认为是其中最卓越的大师。</Source><Target>Unter ihnen galt Xuan Zang als einer der führenden und begabtesten Schüler. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794692</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>13</Serial><Id>1093266794763</Id><Source>他被指定为唐代官方译经院的负责人， </Source><Target>Er wurde zum Leiter des kaiserlichen Übersetzungszentrums der Tang-Dynastie ernannt. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794763</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>14</Serial><Id>1093266794853</Id><Source>他设计并实施了一套翻译工作流程，以确保最后译作的质量。</Source><Target>Er entwickelte und führte einen Übersetzungsablauf ein, mit dem die Qualität des Endprodukts garantiert wurde. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794853</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>15</Serial><Id>1093266794974</Id><Source>下面所列的详细步骤是值得让当今任何翻译队伍采纳借鉴的。</Source><Target>Das im Folgenden aufgeschlüsselte Verfahren ist es wert, von modernen Übersetzungsteams aufgegriffen zu werden.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794974</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>16</Serial><Id>1093266795125</Id><Source>第一步</Source><Target>Stufe 1</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795125</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>17</Serial><Id>1093266795138</Id><Source>由主译和佛教专家共同研讨梵经义理，并解释梵语经文。</Source><Target>Chefübersetzer und Buddhismusexperten studieren und legen gemeinsam den Originaltext in Sanskrit aus. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795138</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>18</Serial><Id>1093266795269</Id><Source>此过程需要一个或更多的人参与。</Source><Target>Das können eine oder mehrere Personen sein.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795269</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>19</Serial><Id>1093266795322</Id><Source>第二步</Source><Target>Stufe 2</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795322</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>20</Serial><Id>1093266795337</Id><Source>翻译队伍的所有成员吟诵经文，由主译提问。</Source><Target>Alle Mitarbeiter des Übersetzungsteams wohnen der Lesung des betreffenden Textes durch den Chefübersetzer bei. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795337</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>21</Serial><Id>1093266795525</Id><Source>其目的是检验第一步中解释的准确性。</Source><Target>Dies dient der Sicherung der Genauigkeit der in Stufe 1 gewonnenen Auslegung. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795525</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>22</Serial><Id>1093266795617</Id><Source>因为经文最初就是用于吟诵的，所以此过程尤显必要。</Source><Target>Der Vortrag des Textes ist notwendig, da die Schriften ursprünglich zum Vorlesen gedacht waren.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795617</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>23</Serial><Id>1093266795725</Id><Source>第三步</Source><Target>Stufe 3</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795725</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>24</Serial><Id>1093266795739</Id><Source>由初级翻译人员第一次将梵语经文翻译成汉语初稿， </Source><Target>Ein Team von Übersetzern erstellt den ersten chinesischen Entwurf des Sanskrit-Textes. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795739</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>25</Serial><Id>1093266795838</Id><Source>该初稿包含梵文术语的音译和标准汉语。</Source><Target>Der Entwurf enthält eine Mischung an transliterierten Sanskrit-Begriffen und Standardchinesisch.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795838</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>26</Serial><Id>1093266795952</Id><Source>第四步</Source><Target>Stufe 4</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795952</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>27</Serial><Id>1093266796006</Id><Source>由一位母语为汉语的高僧负责将全部的汉语译文整理成经文。</Source><Target>Erarbeitung einer vollständig chinesischen Version durch einen erfahrenen buddhistischen Mönch, dessen Muttersprache Chinesisch ist und der in der Übersetzung heiliger Schriften geschult ist. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796006</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>28</Serial><Id>1093266796174</Id><Source>这是所有步骤中最重要的一步，必须由一位深晓中国文化和语言的佛教大师负责。</Source><Target>Dies ist die wichtigste Stufe des gesamten Verfahrens. Diese Aufgabe obliegt einem Mönch, der über umfangreiche und tiefgreifende Kenntnisse der chinesischen Kultur und Sprache verfügt.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796174</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>29</Serial><Id>1093266796351</Id><Source>第五步</Source><Target>Stufe 5</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796351</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>30</Serial><Id>1093266796367</Id><Source>将最后中文译文的句子结构进行润色加工， </Source><Target>Ausarbeitung der Satzstruktur der vollständigen chinesischen Version. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796367</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>31</Serial><Id>1093266796460</Id><Source>这一步非常必要，因为在源语言与目标语言之间存在巨大的语言差异。</Source><Target>Die Notwendigkeit dieser Stufe ergibt sich aus den immensen sprachlichen Unterschieden zwischen Ursprungs- und Zielsprache.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796460</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>32</Serial><Id>1093266796587</Id><Source>第六步</Source><Target>Stufe 6</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796587</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>33</Serial><Id>1093266796604</Id><Source>为确保原文翻译的准确性，将中文译文翻回梵语。</Source><Target>Übersetzung der chinesischen Version in Sanskrit, um die Genauigkeit der Übertragung des Ursprungstextes zu überprüfen. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796604</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>34</Serial><Id>1093266796755</Id><Source>翻译中的错误可以迅速地在译文中得以纠正。</Source><Target>Fehler in der Übertragung müssen in der chinesischen Version unverzüglich berichtigt werden.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796755</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>35</Serial><Id>1093266796864</Id><Source>第七步</Source><Target>Stufe 7</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796864</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>36</Serial><Id>1093266796880</Id><Source>再次检查校验后的中文译文，找出措词不当处，将语言表达得更加明确精炼，提高其可读性。</Source><Target>Nachbearbeitung der überprüften chinesischen Version zur Ermittlung falsch verwendeter Zeichen, zur Verfeinerung des sprachlichen Ausdrucks und damit zur Verbesserung der Lesbarkeit.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796880</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>37</Serial><Id>1093266797078</Id><Source>第八步</Source><Target>Stufe 8</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797078</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>38</Serial><Id>1093266797098</Id><Source>再次将译文进行润色，增强其语言的文学欣赏性，并对单调部分加以修饰。</Source><Target>Letzter Schliff, um die literarische Schönheit der Sprache zu verbessern und um ansonsten eintönigen Schriften Farbigkeit zu geben.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797098</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>39</Serial><Id>1093266797242</Id><Source>第九步</Source><Target>Stufe 9</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797242</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>40</Serial><Id>1093266797261</Id><Source>通过大声朗读译文，确定译文的听觉质量。</Source><Target>Überprüfung der Klanggefälligkeit durch eine Lesung der Übersetzung. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797261</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>41</Serial><Id>1093266797353</Id><Source>音效是很重要的，因为经文是用于讲述给听众的。</Source><Target>Die akustische Wirkung ist wichtig, da die Schriften zur Predigt vor einer Zuhörerschaft vorgesehen sind.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797353</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>42</Serial><Id>1093266797464</Id><Source>第十步</Source><Target>Stufe 10</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797464</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>43</Serial><Id>1093266797482</Id><Source>由主译最后检查译文。</Source><Target>Letzte Prüfung durch den Chefübersetzer.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797482</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>44</Serial><Id>1093266797537</Id><Source>总结</Source><Target>Schlussbemerkung</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040705T121341Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797537</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>45</Serial><Id>1093266797565</Id><Source>玄奘为佛经的翻译做出了巨大的贡献。</Source><Target>Xuan Zang hat für die Übersetzung der buddhistischen Sutras Bedeutendes geleistet. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797565</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>46</Serial><Id>1093266797652</Id><Source>这不仅在于他是一个杰出的语言学家，而且他作为一个虔诚的佛教徒，凭着对佛经的超凡的理解力，将全身心投入到这项事业中。</Source><Target>Er tat sich nicht nur als außergewöhnlicher Linguist hervor, sondern widmete sich auch als ergebener Buddhist mit einem überragenden inhaltlichen Verständnis dieser Aufgabe von ganzem Herzen. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101705Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797652</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>47</Serial><Id>1093266797842</Id><Source>他为这项工程投入了十三年时间。</Source><Target>Er hat dieser Arbeit dreizehn Jahre seines Lebens gewidmet. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797842</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>48</Serial><Id>1093266797899</Id><Source>这已不仅仅是将一种语言翻译成另外一种语言。</Source><Target>Und die Aufgabe bestand nicht lediglich darin, eine Sprache in eine andere zu übertragen. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797899</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>49</Serial><Id>1093266797991</Id><Source>为了有效地传播佛教，中文版的佛经必须被中国的信徒所读懂。</Source><Target>Um den Buddhismus wirkungsvoll zu verbreiten, mussten die chinesischsprachigen Sutras von den chinesischen Gläubigen wirklich verstanden werden. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101717Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797991</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>50</Serial><Id>1093266798115</Id><Source>换句话说，他必须考虑这个群体。</Source><Target>Mit anderen Worten, er musste den Absatzmarkt in Betracht ziehen: </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798115</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>51</Serial><Id>1093266798174</Id><Source>是为那些为佛教提供财政支持的上层阶级服务，还是为那些没有太多文化修养的普通百姓服务，以扩展佛教的影响范围，或者两者兼顾？</Source><Target>Waren die Übersetzungen für den Adel gedacht, von dessen finanzieller Unterstützung der Buddhismus abhängig war, oder für die weniger gebildete breite Bevölkerung, um den Marktanteil zu erhöhen? Oder für beide?</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>de</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101647Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798174</Prop></Pair>
</Asset>
<Asset package="..\..\Samples\XuanZang.tmx" original="zh-cn - en" source-lang="zh-cn" target-lang="en">
<Pair><Serial>1</Serial><Id>1093266792948</Id><Source>玄奘，中国最伟大的翻译家</Source><Target>Xuan Zang, Possibly China's Greatest Translator</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020919T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266792948</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>2</Serial><Id>1093266793131</Id><Source>1300 多年前，他创立了翻译质量控制的十个步骤，其严谨与精确程度远远超过当今翻译界。</Source><Target>His 10-stage quality control process initiated more than 1300 years ago is far more thorough and exacting than any existing today.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793131</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>3</Serial><Id>1093266793344</Id><Source>简介</Source><Target>Introduction</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793344</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>4</Serial><Id>1093266793385</Id><Source>古今中外，几乎无人不晓唐代高僧玄奘在古代汉语方面所做的贡献，以及他在小说《西游记》中的三位徒弟，大徒弟孙悟空，二徒弟猪八戒和三徒弟沙僧。</Source><Target>Every Chinese, young and old, within and outside China, knows the classical language rendering of the exploits of Xuan Zang, the pious Tang dynasty monk and his three storybook disciples, the indestructible Monkey King, the Great Sage; Brother Pig, the Eight Denials (of Buddhism) and Sand Monk, the third disciple. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793385</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>5</Serial><Id>1093266793776</Id><Source>在真实生活中，玄奘的确是一个了不起的僧人。</Source><Target>In real life, Xuan Zang was a truly remarkable Buddhist monk. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793776</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>6</Serial><Id>1093266793860</Id><Source>他突破重重关隘，横渡渺无人烟的地区，直到印度次大陆的佛教发源地，然后带着一套佛教经典回到长安（现西安）。</Source><Target>He traveled on land on the way through hostile and uncharted territory to the birthplace of Buddha in the Indian sub-continent and returned to Chang'an (modern day Xi'an) with a set of Buddhist sutras. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266793860</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>7</Serial><Id>1093266794053</Id><Source>这套卷帙浩繁的佛经是用极难懂的梵语所著。</Source><Target>The voluminous set of sutras was written in the extremely difficult Sanskrit language. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794053</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>8</Serial><Id>1093266794192</Id><Source>他与他的高徒一起将 75 卷佛经翻译成同等难度的汉语。</Source><Target>Together with his doyens of pupils, he completed the translation of some 75 volumes of the sutras into the equally difficult Chinese languages</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794192</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>9</Serial><Id>1093266794333</Id><Source>10 个步骤</Source><Target>The 10 Stages</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794333</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>10</Serial><Id>1093266794352</Id><Source>唐朝以前，汉译佛经颇令人费解，因为最初的译者是非汉族血统的和尚。</Source><Target>Buddhist sutras translated into Chinese prior the Tang dynasty were difficult to comprehend because the first translators were Buddhist monks of non-Han Chinese origin. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794352</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>11</Serial><Id>1093266794516</Id><Source>几百年后，才出现了一批和尚，他们既精通梵文，又深晓复杂的梵经义理。</Source><Target>It took China several hundred years to bring forth a selection of Buddhist monks who could master both the Sanskrit language as well as the complex Buddhism doctrines, which were written in Sanskrit. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794516</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>12</Serial><Id>1093266794692</Id><Source>而玄奘被公认为是其中最卓越的大师。</Source><Target>And Xuan Zang was recognized as foremost among them. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794692</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>13</Serial><Id>1093266794763</Id><Source>他被指定为唐代官方译经院的负责人， </Source><Target>He was appointed chief of the Tang dynasty imperial translation center. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794763</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>14</Serial><Id>1093266794853</Id><Source>他设计并实施了一套翻译工作流程，以确保最后译作的质量。</Source><Target>It was he who designed and implemented a translation workflow that would guarantee the quality of the final product. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794853</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>15</Serial><Id>1093266794974</Id><Source>下面所列的详细步骤是值得让当今任何翻译队伍采纳借鉴的。</Source><Target>The process detailed below is well worth adopting by any modern day translation team.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266794974</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>16</Serial><Id>1093266795125</Id><Source>第一步</Source><Target>Stage 1</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795125</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>17</Serial><Id>1093266795138</Id><Source>由主译和佛教专家共同研讨梵经义理，并解释梵语经文。</Source><Target>Master translator and Buddhism expert to jointly study and interpret the original text written in Sanskrit. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795138</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>18</Serial><Id>1093266795269</Id><Source>此过程需要一个或更多的人参与。</Source><Target>It could involve one or more persons.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795269</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>19</Serial><Id>1093266795322</Id><Source>第二步</Source><Target>Stage 2</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795322</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>20</Serial><Id>1093266795337</Id><Source>翻译队伍的所有成员吟诵经文，由主译提问。</Source><Target>All members of the translation team to attend a recital of the text in question by the Master translator. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795337</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>21</Serial><Id>1093266795525</Id><Source>其目的是检验第一步中解释的准确性。</Source><Target>The purpose is to verify the accuracy of the interpretation undertaken in Stage 1. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795525</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>22</Serial><Id>1093266795617</Id><Source>因为经文最初就是用于吟诵的，所以此过程尤显必要。</Source><Target>A recital is necessary because the scriptures were originally written for recitation.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795617</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>23</Serial><Id>1093266795725</Id><Source>第三步</Source><Target>Stage 3</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795725</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>24</Serial><Id>1093266795739</Id><Source>由初级翻译人员第一次将梵语经文翻译成汉语初稿， </Source><Target>A team of junior translators produces the first Chinese draft of the Sanskrit text. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795739</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>25</Serial><Id>1093266795838</Id><Source>该初稿包含梵文术语的音译和标准汉语。</Source><Target>The draft is a combination of transliteration of Sanskrit terms and standard Chinese.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795838</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>26</Serial><Id>1093266795952</Id><Source>第四步</Source><Target>Stage 4</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266795952</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>27</Serial><Id>1093266796006</Id><Source>由一位母语为汉语的高僧负责将全部的汉语译文整理成经文。</Source><Target>Production of a complete Chinese version by a senior native Chinese Buddhist monk trained to undertake scripture translation. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796006</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>28</Serial><Id>1093266796174</Id><Source>这是所有步骤中最重要的一步，必须由一位深晓中国文化和语言的佛教大师负责。</Source><Target>This is the most important stage in the entire process and it must be undertaken by a monk with an in-depth knowledge of Chinese culture and language.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796174</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>29</Serial><Id>1093266796351</Id><Source>第五步</Source><Target>Stage 5</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796351</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>30</Serial><Id>1093266796367</Id><Source>将最后中文译文的句子结构进行润色加工， </Source><Target>Refinement of sentence structure of the complete Chinese version. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796367</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>31</Serial><Id>1093266796460</Id><Source>这一步非常必要，因为在源语言与目标语言之间存在巨大的语言差异。</Source><Target>This is a necessary stage because of the vast linguistic differences between the source and target language.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796460</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>32</Serial><Id>1093266796587</Id><Source>第六步</Source><Target>Stage 6</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796587</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>33</Serial><Id>1093266796604</Id><Source>为确保原文翻译的准确性，将中文译文翻回梵语。</Source><Target>Reverse translation of the Chinese version into Sanskrit in order to verify the accuracy of the interpretation of the original text. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796604</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>34</Serial><Id>1093266796755</Id><Source>翻译中的错误可以迅速地在译文中得以纠正。</Source><Target>Mistakes in interpretation are to be promptly rectified in the Chinese version.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796755</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>35</Serial><Id>1093266796864</Id><Source>第七步</Source><Target>Stage 7</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796864</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>36</Serial><Id>1093266796880</Id><Source>再次检查校验后的中文译文，找出措词不当处，将语言表达得更加明确精炼，提高其可读性。</Source><Target>Review of the verified Chinese version to identify errors in character usage, and refinement of linguistic expressions to improve readability.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266796880</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>37</Serial><Id>1093266797078</Id><Source>第八步</Source><Target>Stage 8</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797078</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>38</Serial><Id>1093266797098</Id><Source>再次将译文进行润色，增强其语言的文学欣赏性，并对单调部分加以修饰。</Source><Target>Further polishing to improve the literary beauty of the language and adding colors to the otherwise monotonous writings.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797098</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>39</Serial><Id>1093266797242</Id><Source>第九步</Source><Target>Stage 9</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797242</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>40</Serial><Id>1093266797261</Id><Source>通过大声朗读译文，确定译文的听觉质量。</Source><Target>Verification of the audio quality by reciting the translation aloud. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797261</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>41</Serial><Id>1093266797353</Id><Source>音效是很重要的，因为经文是用于讲述给听众的。</Source><Target>The audio effect is important because scriptures are meant for preaching to an audience.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797353</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>42</Serial><Id>1093266797464</Id><Source>第十步</Source><Target>Stage 10</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797464</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>43</Serial><Id>1093266797482</Id><Source>由主译最后检查译文。</Source><Target>Final check by the Master Translator.</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797482</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>44</Serial><Id>1093266797537</Id><Source>总结</Source><Target>Conclusion</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040705T121341Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797537</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>45</Serial><Id>1093266797565</Id><Source>玄奘为佛经的翻译做出了巨大的贡献。</Source><Target>Xuan Zang did a great job in the translation of the Buddhist sutras. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797565</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>46</Serial><Id>1093266797652</Id><Source>这不仅在于他是一个杰出的语言学家，而且他作为一个虔诚的佛教徒，凭着对佛经的超凡的理解力，将全身心投入到这项事业中。</Source><Target>He was able to excel not only was he an outstanding linguist but also he was wholeheartedly committed to the task as a devoted Buddhist with an extraordinary understanding of its contents. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101705Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797652</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>47</Serial><Id>1093266797842</Id><Source>他为这项工程投入了十三年时间。</Source><Target>Indeed, he dedicated thirteen years of his life to the task. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797842</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>48</Serial><Id>1093266797899</Id><Source>这已不仅仅是将一种语言翻译成另外一种语言。</Source><Target>And the task was not simply transforming one language into another. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797899</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>49</Serial><Id>1093266797991</Id><Source>为了有效地传播佛教，中文版的佛经必须被中国的信徒所读懂。</Source><Target>In order to effectively spread Buddhism, the sutras in Chinese would have to be understood by the Chinese devotees. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101717Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266797991</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>50</Serial><Id>1093266798115</Id><Source>换句话说，他必须考虑这个群体。</Source><Target>In other words, he had to take into account the marketplace. </Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798115</Prop></Pair>
<Pair><Serial>51</Serial><Id>1093266798174</Id><Source>是为那些为佛教提供财政支持的上层阶级服务，还是为那些没有太多文化修养的普通百姓服务，以扩展佛教的影响范围，或者两者兼顾？</Source><Target>Was it intended for the gentry for whom Buddhism depended for their financial support or was it for the less literate general populace to widen market share or was it for both?</Target><SourceLang>zh-cn</SourceLang><TargetLang>en</TargetLang><Prop name="changedate">20040823T101647Z</Prop><Prop name="creationdate">20020930T004233Z</Prop><Prop name="creationid">Mike Du</Prop><Prop name="tuid">1093266798174</Prop></Pair>
</Asset>
